Package GUI.src

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Gui
    The Gui class contains the entire FXML based GUI including all functionalities.
    Klima
    The Klima class for the temperature display.
    Licht
    The Licht class contains all logical functionalities and graphical displays of lights in rooms.
    Lichtpop
    Lichtpop class for the light configuration pop-up
    Modul
    The Modul class contains the current light and temperature data of the module in a room, it is updated with data received from the WSN.
    Raum
    The Raum class contains all the variables for a room (such as Licht, Modul and Klima), as well as a constructor.
    Schnittstelle
    The Schnittstelle class is used for connecting a device to a USB-port, as well as handling wireless communications over a connected device later on.
    Temppop
    Temppop class for the temperature configuration pop-up
    ToggleSwitch
    The ToggleSwitch class is used to create toggle switches in the GUI of the temperature and light pop-ups.
